1.Introduction to Problem/Motivation : Muc tieu
	-	Anh xa muc tieu nghien cuu sang cong viec nghien cuu.
	-	Dua ra nhung cau hoi can dc giai quye trong de tai (hay hon)
	
2. Reasearh Objectives:
	-	Cong viec thuc su phu thuoc vao no luc
	-	Muc tieu cang cu the , cang sat voi muc tieu de ra. (Muc tieu ro rang, chi tiet )
	-	
3. Research Plan:	Method vs Solution.
	
	-	PP nghien cuu : nganh minh la mo phong.
	-	Phai chung minh pp do phu hop voi bai toan va mang lai ket qua tinh cay va o muc do nao ,(bao ve pp minh lam).
	-	PP nghien cuu khac voi giai phap .
	-	Dung 1 giai phap va lay 1 pp nghien cuu de danh gia lai muc do hoan hao cua sp do .

		Ex:	pp chung minh la sp (1 cai mo hinh xe) co the dat dc ket luan (480KM/H).

	-	Reasearch plan 
	-	Overall Schedule : giai doan thiet ke, ra san pham, ra bao cao.
	-	Outline thesis : suy nghi, cau truc luan van mang tinh chat goi nho (options)

		+	Xac dinh van de nghien cuu
		+	Dang de nghien cuu
		+	Co kha nang giai quyet , (tai ieu nghien cuu co huong di - giai phap de ra san)

		+	De cuong tot, ro rang se theo dung ket hoach.(50% cong viec, co kha nang thuc hien).


	1.	Observation:	
		+	bai toan xuat phat tu dau,
		+	La diem xuat phat cho bai toan .
	2.	Literature reviews:
		+	Doc rut ra cac dac trung, giai phap va tim ra huong moi de giai quyet.
	3.	Define research objectives:
		+	What to achieve:	chi ro ra dieu giai quyet dc trong 1 dong van de, muc tieu giai quyet 1 phan trong bai toan rat lon.	
		+	Question to be answered:	
	4.	Develop research plan:
		

